BEGIN_PGML


Find the equation for the circle with center [` ([$h],[$k]) `] and passes through [` ([$a],[$b]) `].

 [_______________] [`=`] [_____________][@ helpLink("numbers") @]*


 [$video]*
END_PGML

 BEGIN_TEXT
